@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ritjit(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v0 * wp.abs((v1 + 0.43 * tmp + 0.24)))
    tmp = 0.01
    v2 = (0.68 - ((v2 + 0.51 / v0 + 0.43) - 0.43))
    v2 = 0.69
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.37 + v0 + 0.26) + (v1 + 0.73 * v1 + 0.84)) / v0)
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.10)))
    tmp = 0.87
    data[tid] = v0
